description:
RxWebKit is a RxSwift wrapper for `WebKit`.

```swift
// MARK: Setup WKWebView

let webView = WKWebView(frame: self.view.bounds)
self.view.addSubview(webView)


// MARK: Observing properties

webView.rx_title
    .subscribeNext {
        print("title: ($0)")
    }
    .addDisposableTo(disposeBag)

webView.rx_URL
    .subscribeNext {
        print("URL: ($0)")
    }
    .addDisposableTo(disposeBag)
```
